<div class="mf-hero"><div class="mf-hero__bg" if="" section.settings.hero_image="" style="background-image:url({{ section.settings.hero_image | image_url: width: 2000 }})" endif=""></div><div class="mf-hero__overlay"></div><div class="mf-hero__content"><div class="mf-hero__label">Educational Resource</div><h1>Understanding <em>Male Infertility</em></h1><p class="mf-hero__sub">Understanding male fertility is the first step. LogixX Fertility provides clinically proven diagnostics and treatments to support you and your partner on your journey to conceive.</p><div class="mf-hero__pills"><div class="mf-hero__pill"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00C2B8" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>Clinically Proven</div><div class="mf-hero__pill"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00C2B8" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>Expert Guidance</div><div class="mf-hero__pill"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00C2B8" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>Advanced Diagnostics</div></div><div class="mf-hero__stats"><div class="mf-hero__stat"><span class="mf-hero__stat-num">1 in 7</span><span class="mf-hero__stat-lbl">UK Couples</span></div><div class="mf-hero__stat-div"></div><div class="mf-hero__stat"><span class="mf-hero__stat-num">50%</span><span class="mf-hero__stat-lbl">Male Factor</span></div><div class="mf-hero__stat-div"></div><div class="mf-hero__stat"><span class="mf-hero__stat-num">85%</span><span class="mf-hero__stat-lbl">Conceive Naturally</span></div></div></div></div>
<div class="mf-stats"><div class="mf-stat"><div class="mf-stat__icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"></path></svg></div><div class="mf-stat__num">1 in 7</div><div class="mf-stat__label">UK Couples Affected</div><div class="mf-stat__sub">Approximately 3.5 million people in the UK are unable to have a child</div></div><div class="mf-stat"><div class="mf-stat__icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line></svg></div><div class="mf-stat__num">50%</div><div class="mf-stat__label">Male Factor</div><div class="mf-stat__sub">In 50% of cases the problem lies wholly or partly with the male partner</div></div><div class="mf-stat"><div class="mf-stat__icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg></div><div class="mf-stat__num">85%</div><div class="mf-stat__label">Conceive Naturally</div><div class="mf-stat__sub">Many couples conceive whilst undergoing investigations within the first year</div></div></div>
<div class="mf-section"><div class="mf-section-header"><div class="mf-section-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line></svg></div><h2>When Should I Seek Help?</h2></div><div class="mf-card"><p>If you have been trying unsuccessfully to produce a pregnancy for <strong>1–2 years without using contraception</strong>, you should contact your GP for further advice. Your GP will normally wish to review you and your partner together.</p><p>Further investigations may reveal that only one partner has a problem. Urological investigations are essential in revealing reversible underlying causes for male-factor subfertility and full assessment by a urologist is recommended in all cases.</p></div><div class="mf-note"><strong>Important:</strong> Not all advanced tests for Male Fertility Assessment are available on the NHS — such as Sperm Oxidative Stress tests or Sperm DNA Fragmentation tests. Current NICE guidance on Male Fertility may not reflect current advances in urological medical knowledge available in the private sector.</div></div>
<div class="mf-section"><div class="mf-section-header"><div class="mf-section-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z"></path><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"></line><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line></svg></div><h2>Causes of Male Infertility</h2></div><div class="mf-card"><p>In <strong>75% of infertile men</strong>, the cause remains unexplained — termed "idiopathic infertility". It may still be possible for couples to conceive naturally, provided some sperm are present.</p></div><div class="mf-grid2"><div class="mf-cause-card"><div class="mf-cause-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1"></path><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8z"></path><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"></line><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"></line><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"></line></svg></div><h4>Lifestyle Factors</h4><p>Smoking, excessive alcohol, recreational drugs, gym supplements and excessive heat exposure from saunas, hot baths and laptops on your lap</p></div><div class="mf-cause-card"><div class="mf-cause-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path></svg></div><h4>Hormonal Issues</h4><p>Imbalances in thyroid, prolactin, FSH, LH or testosterone — including pituitary disease, hypothalamic conditions and defective testosterone synthesis</p></div><div class="mf-cause-card"><div class="mf-cause-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"></path><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"></line><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"></line></svg></div><h4>Physical Causes</h4><p>Varicocele, previous testicular infection or surgery, undescended testis, obstruction or blockage of sperm transport at any stage of delivery</p></div><div class="mf-cause-card"><div class="mf-cause-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 002 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0021 16z"></path></svg></div><h4>Genetic Factors</h4><p>Chromosomal abnormalities such as Klinefelter's syndrome, Y chromosome micro-deletions and cystic fibrosis gene mutations associated with infertility</p></div></div></div>
